# Digital Ocean App Platform - SPA Configuration
# This ensures proper routing for Single Page Applications

# All routes should serve index.html
# This fixes 404 errors for /aprovado, /produto/*, etc.

# Configuration applied:
# 1. catchall_document: index.html
# 2. error_document: index.html  
# 3. Specific routes defined for main paths
# 4. _redirects and static.json for fallback

# Expected behavior:
# https://burgz.food/ -> index.html (200)
# https://burgz.food/produto/4 -> index.html (200) 
# https://burgz.food/aprovado -> index.html (200)
# React Router handles client-side routing